result.title: ACM-ICPC World Finals 2016
result.content:
ACM-ICPC World Finals 2016 will take place on May, 19, 03:00 (UTC). It is one of the most important events in programming competitions life.

More than 40000 contestants from 2736 universitites from 102 countries had competed in regional competitions. 128 teams had advanced to the World Finals, which are held this year in Phuket, Thailand. Soon we will know which university takes home the most prestigious title in programming â€” the tile of the World Champion of ACM ICPC!
